@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_trrhqc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.sin(v2 + 0.94) / (tmp + 0.80 - v0 + 0.22)))
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.84 - v0 + 0.60) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.18)) * v0)
    v0 = v2
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.49 - tmp + 0.36)) / v2)
    tmp = 0.67
    data[tid] = v0
